	('Faron Korok Seed 1', 'Sparkle Cloud', '0353, -2000, 0008', 'Inside the hollow of a tree trunk in the Deya Village Ruins, there will be a whirlwind of leaves hovering around. Examine it to reveal a Korok.', 1458),
	('Faron Korok Seed 2', 'Sparkle Cloud', '0166, -1942, 0045', 'West of the Deya Village Ruins, there is a small forest with a big tree in the middle of it. Near the tree there will be two statues that will require of you to offer two apples. One apple is already set in one statue, so that leaves you to offer the remaining red apple.', 1459),
