	('Faron Korok Seed 34', 'Pop the Cork', '0100, -3839, 0031', 'Near the shores of Puffer Beach, there will be a tall platform on which a Korok cork stands. Use the nearby rocks to attach the cork and give it weight enough for the Korok to uncover.', 1491),
