	('Great Hyrule Forest Korok Seed 11+12', 'Reunite Friends', '-0325, 3158, 0099', 'In the Drenan Highlands, you can find a Korok that needs to be delivered to their friend up a hill to the East. There doesn\'t seem to be any devices nearby you can use, so consider bring a horse or having autobuild ready to build a vehicle.', 1537),
	('Great Hyrule Forest Korok Seed 13+14', 'Reunite Friends', '0523, 3397, 0184', 'Northeast of Thyphlo Ruins, you can find a Korok that needs to be taken downhill to their friend. Use a cart found nearby.', 1538),
