	('Great Hyrule Forest Korok Seed 21+22', 'Sparkle Cloud', '-0544, 2225, 0268', 'Atop the hill of Aldor Foothills, down south from the tip of Mount Drena, you can find a Korok that needs delivering far to the west. Luckily it\'s downhill, so grab a nearby cart and send them dow.', 1545),
